{
  "name": "07-pools-of-storage-functional-spec-597fa5",
  "title": "Pools of Storage Decision Tool \u2014 Functional Specification (Aberdeen Internal)",
  "description": "Internal Aberdeen Group functional specification for the Pools of Storage Decision Tool \u2014 explicitly marked 'Do Not Share With Maxtor.' Version 1.0 dated November 25 2003 describing a guided decision support web application built in Microsoft ASP/SQL Server 2000 targeting Internet Explorer 5.5+ on Windows. The tool has four stages: Solution Workflow (recommend business process); Competitive Workflow (maturity grid positioning); Financial Framework (KPI analysis); and Case for Action (ROI/TCO calculation with PDF output). Planned development cost $23101.55 over 6 weeks with Aberdeen hosting 3 months.",
